modName: Zulfarr - A male khajiit lvl 13 NO CHEATS
summary: This is my second own savegame. I called him Zulfarr, and he\'s a male khajiit.
descriptionHtml:
Zulfarr is a male khajiit who isn\'t trained in anything. I mean, all skills are balanced so, decide what you want to be!

It\'s a savegame for people who want to do more quests in the game and train the char.

- College of Winterhold Complete.
- Breezehome bought and fully equiped.
- Found the Amulet of Mara (I don\'t bought it, I found it).
- He has no wife :(

Instalation:

Put the .ess and .ess.bak (both) files in /Documents (or My Documents)/My Games/Skyrim/Saves

If anything comes up let me know it. If you have a problem, send me a message.

I don\'t remember the mods i used, i think there are the same than my other savegame (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24245), but if there\'s anything new let me know so I can credit the author.

By the way, if you don\'t like the khajiits or the name you just can change it typing \"showracemenu\" in console.
author: elv14
